shopping /ˈʃɒpɪŋ/

1. N-UNCOUNT When you do the shopping , you go to the stores or shops and buy things. 购物 

例： I'll do the shopping this afternoon. 我今天下午要去购物。 

2. N-UNCOUNT Your shopping is the things that you have bought from stores, especially food. 从商店买回来的东西 (尤指食品) [英国英语]

